# Environment variables — copy to .env and adjust for local development.
# Never commit .env (the pre-commit hook blocks it).
#
# Prefer Bun.secrets: bun secrets set com.kimi.<app>/<name> <value>
# Optional registry: bun run scripts/postinstall.ts --with-secrets
# Env fallbacks use UPPER_SNAKE_CASE keys when Bun.secrets is unavailable.

# ── Optional ──
# PORT=0                    # 0 = auto-assign. Override only if needed.
# LOG_LEVEL=info            # debug | info | warn | error
# NODE_ENV=development      # development | test | production
